 {"type":"message","id":"6adb323e","parentId":"f4f5a82e","timestamp":"2026-03-29T05:27:12.400Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All 4 checks pass. 43 test files, 778 tests pass (19 new tests added).\n\n---\n\n## What I implemented\n\n### `frontend/src/components/shared/usePersistedState.ts`\nA generic React hook that:\n- Reads from `localStorage` in the `useState` initializer (runs synchronously before first render, avoiding flicker)\n- Uses `JSON.parse`/`JSON.stringify` for type-safe serialization\n- Writes back to localStorage in a `useEffect` whenever the value changes\n- Silently ignores errors (private browsing, storage quota, etc.)\n\n### `frontend/src/components/shared/CollapsibleSection.tsx`\nA collapsible section component with:\n- **localStorage persistence** via `usePersistedState` under key `wc-section-{id}`\n- **`defaultExpanded` prop** — used on first visit (before localStorage has a value)\n- **Accessible header button** with `aria-expanded`, `aria-controls`, and `type=\"button\"`\n- **Content div** with `role=\"region\"` and `aria-labelledby`\n- **Smooth CSS grid height transition** (`gridTemplateRows: 0fr ↔ 1fr`) with `overflow-hidden` on the direct grid child\n- **Optional badge** rendered inline next to the title\n- **Consistent styling** with the Card/CardHeader pattern (border-border, bg-surface, px-4 py-3)\n- **`className` prop** for customisation\n\n### `frontend/src/__tests__/CollapsibleSection.test.tsx`\n19 tests covering:\n- Title and children rendering, badge presence/absence\n- `defaultExpanded` true/false/default\n- Toggle behaviour (expand → collapse → expand)\n- localStorage write (collapsed state, expanded state)\n- localStorage read priority over `defaultExpanded`\n- Full accessibility: `aria-controls`, `aria-labelledby`, `role=\"region\"`, button type\n- Outer wrapper testid and custom className\n\n### Checks\n- ✅ `typecheck` — clean\n- ✅ `lint` — 0 errors (13 pre-existing warnings)\n- ✅ `unit` — 778/778 pass (19 new)\n- ✅ `build` — successful\n\nVerdict: changes_made"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":548,"cacheRead":166527,"cacheWrite":216,"totalTokens":167292,"cost":{"input":0.000003,"output":0.00822,"cacheRead":0.0499581,"cacheWrite":0.0008100000000000001,"total":0.0589911}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774762019854,"responseId":"msg_01DdXUS7zTLVr1LUqNr9U92U"}}
